2 eggs
1 cup of milk
 
Beat these two ingredients together.
 
1 cup flour
1/2 tsp. salt
1 tsp. melted margarine/butter
 
Mix all together with a beater.  Let stand in room temperature for 1 to 3 hours before using for best results.  Put in muffin tins that has dripping/grease from meat or crisco shortening on the bottom.  Heat the fat first.  Beat the mixture a little just before putting in muffin tins.  Add mixture to hot fat and bake at 450 degrees for 20 - 25 minutes.
 
